column12:
'desc': [u'

Farlin Orthodontic - Glow in Dark Price: Rs.175

Every new parent has been jolted out of bed in the middle of the night by the cries of their baby. As you get to your baby’s room
column13: half asleep and jostled by your baby\u2019s sharp crying
column14:
you find it almost impossible to locate your little one\u2019s pacifier. Farlin understands how parents can find these midnight tussles absolutely stressful and has created a very practical pacifier that can make life so much simpler. The Farlin Orthodontic - Glow in the Dark pacifier glows in the dark and allows you to find the pacifier in the jiffy and calm your baby in no time. The pacifier renders orthodontic advantages as well.

\r\n

\r\n\tMade from high quality silicone this firm and flexible pacifier promotes the natural development of your baby\u2019s palate
column15:
teeth and gums. The pacifier is soft and easy to suck and reduces pressure on the jaw during sucking. The bulb of the teat is designed to allow proper tongue placement during sucking. The glow-in-the-dark pacifier from Farlin is suitable for babies aged 6 to 8 months. The pacifier is durable and maintains its shape even after long use. The shield of the pacifier has ventilation holes to allow the circulation of air and also has a swivel ring that allows you to take the pacifier out of your baby\u2019s mouth with ease. Now you can enjoy peace and quiet while you put your baby to bed or prepare their bottle and your baby enjoys soothing comfort with the Farlin Orthodontic pacifier.

\n
\n ']

'desc': [u'

Farlin Effort Saving Manual Breast Pump - Manual Price: Rs.2250

The Farlin Effort Saving Manual Breast Pump has been designed to help new mothers express and store breast milk in a safe
column17: hygienic and comfortable manner. The ergonomic manual breast pump can easily be used with one hand and simulates your baby\'s suckling action to naturally encourage let-down and allow you to express breast milk with ease. The soft silicone liner in the breastshield offers comfort and gently massages the breast to promote the milk flow. The practical adjustable dial enables pressure control
column18: offering maximum comfort. The manual breast pump is easy to assemble and has a compact design allowing you to discreetly use the pump at home or even when you travel. The easy-to-use breast pump comes with a 150 cc polypropylene storage container with a cover and can be converted into a nursing bottle with the silicone teat. With the Farlin Effort Saving Manual Breast Pump
column19: you no longer have to depend on loud motors
column21:
instead you can discreetly express breast milk manually and comfortably.

\r\n

\r\n\tIt is recommended to massage the breast and apply hot compress before using the breast pump. The breast pump set must be washed and sterilized before first use and after every use. The storage container can be washed in the dishwasher. The pump seals of the breast pump are heat resistant
column22: however boiling is not recommended as it may affect the elasticity and the suction effect of the pump. The breast milk storage bottle
column25:
screw cover can be cleaned with mild detergent and hot water and can be boiled or steam sterilized to ensure cleanliness and hygiene.

\n

column16:
'desc': [u'

Pigeon Training Toothbrush Lesson-1 (Light Blue) Price: Rs.135

When infants are around six months of age their first milk teeth start to appear. It is mandatory to start their dental hygiene routine in the beginning itself. Though your tiny tot may not be eating any solid food or any food other than mother’s milk there is a high chance of tooth decay from the natural sugars found in breast milk. To prevent this and to ensure that your bundle of joy has the best smile with healthy glistening white teeth you have to clean their teeth regularly. Pigeon’s Training Toothbrush Lesson 1 has been crafted especially for babies of six to eight months of age.

The elastic rubber head of this Pigeon Training Toothbrush will brush gently against your bundle of joy’s tender gums massaging them softly. The handle is made with a very contoured design that makes it easy for you to hold and brush your baby’s teeth with care and precision. When using this toothbrush make sure that the shield is attached so that the brush does not go deep into the infant’s mouth and cause choking.

teeth and gums. The pacifier is soft and easy to suck and reduces pressure on the jaw during sucking. The bulb of the teat is designed to allow proper tongue placement during sucking. The glow-in-the-dark pacifier from Farlin is suitable for babies aged 6 to 8 months. The pacifier is durable and maintains its shape even after long use. The shield of the pacifier has ventilation holes to allow the circulation of air and also has a swivel ring that allows you to take the pacifier out of your baby\u2019s mouth with ease. Now you can enjoy peace and quiet while you put your baby to bed or prepare their bottle and your baby enjoys soothing comfort with the Farlin Orthodontic pacifier.
